column2: SELECT TOP #  a.apogee_id,cast(str(a.glon,#,#) as float) glon,cast(str(a.glat,#,#) as float) glat,a.snr,a.vhelio_avg,a.vscatter,q.teff,q.logg,q.m_h,q.alpha_m  FROM apogeeStar as a  JOIN dbo.fgetNearbyApogeeStarEq(#,#,#) AS b ON b.apstar_id = a.apstar_id  JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id=o.apogee_id  JOIN aspcapStar as q ON a.apstar_id=q.apstar_id  WHERE o.j > # AND o.j < # AND o.h > # AND o.h < # AND o.k > # AND o.k < # AND a.snr > # AND a.snr < # AND a.vhelio_avg > # AND a.vhelio_avg < # AND a.vscatter > # AND a.vscatter < # AND q.teff > # AND q.teff < # AND q.logg > # AND q.logg < # AND q.param_m_h > # AND q.param_m_h < # AND q.param_alpha_m > # AND q.param_alpha_m < #
